{"tid":1359343,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"探討美國獨立宣言嘅歷史","createTime":"2019-07-24T06:20:01.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-25T09:57:01.000Z","uid":136027,"like":37,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"b11af0b30229a2e9b2fee80b64597c839446dc3a","tid":1359343,"uid":136027,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T06:20:01.000Z","msg":"在 1763 年結束的「七年戰爭」中，法國失去了加拿大及自身在歐洲的中心地位，西班牙則放棄了佛羅里達州及其在墨西哥灣的統治地位。可是，即使法國與西班牙早已對強橫的英國咬牙切齒，也不會貿然介入英國的內戰。「獨立宣言」主要起草人 Thomas Jefferson 心裡清楚，美國必須表明是一個獨立國家，才能與其他國家共同對抗英國。<br />\n<br />\n7 月 4 日，當日為星期四，大陸議會通過了「獨立宣言」，翌日便印製好數百份印刷本。直到星期一，議會把複本以快船送往法國，在巴黎的特使則命令把文件從速送到法國法院及西班牙法院。Ferreiro 稱，該文件雖然叫作「獨立宣言」（Declaration of Independence），同時也是對法國及西班牙的「依靠」（dependence）宣言。<br />\n<br />\n「獨立宣言」誕生一年之內，法國就與美國簽署條約，自動參戰；一年後，即使沒有正式與美國結盟，西班牙也協助法國參與戰事。他們把地區戰爭擴戰成世界戰爭，幫助美國擺脫英國統治，結果西班牙從英國人手上重奪了佛羅里達州，而法國則和美國在約克鎮並肩作戰，戰勝英國。Ferreiro 結論稱，若沒有西法兩國的潛在國際盟友，美國最重要的獨立宣言也許不會面世。獨立宣言的真正「初衷」還待歷史學家辯論，但背後說明的道理卻很淺白：獨立講求實力，實力不足便要尋求盟友。<br />\nSource:<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.cup.com.hk/2017/07/04/essence-of-declaration-of-independence/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.cup.com.hk%2F2017%2F07%2F04%2Fessence-of-declaration-of-independence%2F&d=WWcUXgYU4baXfieBSZbTe%2FsUKqL2I5G2E%2FT5UXudKlU%3D&h=698b2311\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.cup.com.hk/2017/07/04/essence-of-declaration-of-independence/</a><br />\n另外睇埋呢個post:<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1354056\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1354056</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b2a41364ba214a290dcb9eda09e9aab4e4b92e3e","tid":1359343,"uid":136027,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T06:27:23.000Z","msg":"自推"},{"pid":"8c3f211d7b86e18020536acaad7db19be927dbcb","tid":1359343,"uid":136027,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T06:31:44.000Z","msg":"PUSH"},{"pid":"8b590d8847f944bb96fe26a65ff46696bbecf6b3","tid":1359343,"uid":136027,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T06:41:00.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"4c2135881a732c28ce879fc2a183b89c1cbb8be4","tid":1359343,"uid":136027,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T06:41:34.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"05b938cdacab7c2e32fa31f33ed391b85c521248","tid":1359343,"uid":136027,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T06:41:44.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"a1717c0a1f0e101be0823c4d030645458da2bcab","tid":1359343,"uid":273186,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T07:26:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"145e3739159bdca19c3bbac1d06596b1c279cbb9","tid":1359343,"uid":117276,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T07:30:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncer.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4b08fc208083f54bcd59cf2865e27dfa48bd2419","tid":1359343,"uid":273186,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T07:30:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e68ca1257baca3de1263e263873f9f9384f49cb9","tid":1359343,"uid":117276,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T07:38:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cf076dfeba9c4d6f08f2ed81f9ec5f6197c28919","tid":1359343,"uid":273186,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T07:39:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"983caec7bbeaca7537ad1cf1b8aa8b45e7b2312d","tid":1359343,"